snippet.title: Dj Ginge Coldwell
snippet.description:
Hi, I'm DJ Ginge Coldwell. I've worked as a DJ, Radio Broadcaster, and Music Promoter professionally for almost 20 years. I'm a veteran of The Royal Air Force Regiment in which I served for over 22 years,

DJ-ing was a passion in my spare time., since leaving the forces in 2000, I formed a company called Fire Trax Sound and Light and ' worked internationally, worked as a Cruise Ship DJ in the USA, the Caribbean and Europe., I've also managed a very sucessful Greek Band called Zante Dilemma.

I now live full time and still work in Greece, in the Summer as a resident DJ for Magdalaners Tsilivi Zakynthos.

I love all styles of music, Jack of all styles, a master of none. Love to promote new talent also.
